# ─── DEVELOPMENT ONLY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file is for LOCAL development on your PC (npm run dev).
# When testing on a MOBILE PHONE on the same WiFi, replace localhost with your
# PC's local IP address, e.g.: VITE_API_URL=http://192.168.1.5:5000/api
# Run `ipconfig` in PowerShell to find your PC's IPv4 address.
#
# For a DEPLOYED/PRODUCTION site, delete VITE_API_URL entirely so the
# app uses the relative /api path (served from the same server as the frontend).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api